name: RED CIRCLE
description:
Beautifully hand-painted on 100% organic cotton.
*Limited Edition*
'RED CIRCLE' design will be retired after 5 editions.

Each shirt is painted when ordered. As with any handmade product, small (and beautiful) variances are to be expected. Available in white, in sizes XS, S, M, L, XL.
*Please measure carefully before you place your order.*

Measure under arms at the fullest part of the chest, and around natural waist. Keep measuring tape comfortably loose. SIZE CHART: XS: chest 30-32", waist 28-30" S: chest 34-36", waist 30-32" M: chest 38-40", waist 32-33" L: chest 42-44", waist 33-34" XL: chest 46-48", waist 36-38"
For ACTUAL shirt dimensions CLICK HERE.

Blank t-shirts manufactured by American Apparel, Sustainable Edition. SUGGESTED SHIRT CARE: For optimum longevity, hand-wash in cool water and hang to dry.
